Frequently Asked Questions

How do I create a new note?

Click the 'Add Note' button on the main page, enter your note title, and save.

Is my data secure?

Yes, your notes are stored securely and only accessible to you.

Can I edit or delete notes?

Currently, you can create and view notes. Editing and deleting features are coming soon.

How do I change the theme?

Theme settings are saved in your browser. You can change them from the settings menu.
